geography of the interior united states.data-term: geography of the interior united states

examples.en: Our company relocated to the Midwest.
The immigrants settled in the Midwest.
The Midwest will experience an intense freeze later in the week.
He spent his youth in the Midwest.
Can you locate your cousins in the Midwest?
Pioneers crossed the American Midwest in wagons.
The word pop for soda is a Midwest regionalism.
Oxidation ponds are extensively used for sewage treatment in the Midwest.
My roommate and I share a common bond because we both grew up in the Midwest.
